Package au.csiro.pathling.fhirpath

Interface Numeric

All Known Implementing Classes:
DecimalCollection, EmptyCollection, IntegerCollection, QuantityCollection, StringCollection
public interface Numeric
Describes a path that represents a numeric value, and can be the subject of math operations.
Author:
John Grimes

      @Nonnull Function<Numeric,Collection> getMathOperation(@Nonnull Numeric.MathOperation operation)

      Parameters:
      operation - The Numeric.MathOperation type to retrieve a result for
      Returns:
